  title `The WASTE-LANDS (CLAIMS) ACT, 1863`
  actNumber (23)
  enactmentDate 1863-03-10
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/19035`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `बंजर भूमि (दावे) अधिनियम,1863`
  actYear (1863)
  ministry `Ministry of Home Affairs`
  department `Department of States`
  longTitle `WHEREAS it is expedient to make special provision for the speedy adjudication of claims which may be preferred to waste lands proposed to be sold, or otherwise dealt with, on account of Government, and of objections taken to the sale or other disposition of such lands ; It is enacted as follows.`
